description:
This is a 46 minute workout called '45 Min Yoga Routine | Full Body Beginner Friendly Yoga' from the channel Charlie Follows.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Welcome to this 45 min full body yoga routine. This class is great for mixed levels and includes a well rounded sequence to build strength, flexibility, and improve balance and coordination. 

This beginner friendly sequence includes options to suit different levels and is intended to give you a complete practice that you can come back to whenever you want a full body flow.

The sequence includes a steady vinyasa flow with sun salutations, hip openers, backbends, standing balances and twists. It's designed to help you feel like you've given your body everything it needs to have a great day. 

I hope you enjoy this full body yoga flow. 

Charlie x
